<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">مُسْلِمَانِ عَدْلَانِ عِنْدَ إِشْكَالِهِ:</span> إِنَّهُ مَخُوفٌ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>- لَا يَلْزَمُ تَبَرُّعُهُ لِوَارِثٍ بِشَيْءٍ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>- وَلَا بِمَا فَوْقَ الثُّلُثِ لِغَيْرِهِ، إِلَّا بِإِجَازَةِ الوَرَثَةِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَمَنِ امْتَدَّ مَرَضُهُ بِجُذَامٍ وَنَحْوِهِ،<span class="c5"> وَلَمْ يَقْطَعْهُ بِفِرَاشٍ:</span> فَكَصَحِيحٍ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>- وَيُعْتَبَرُ عِنْدَ المَوْتِ كَوْنُهُ وَارِثاً أَوْ لَا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> يُبْدَأُ بِالأَوَّلِ فَالأَوَّلِ بِالعَطِيَّةِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَلَا يَصِحُّ الرُّجُوعُ فِيهَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَيُعْتَبَرُ قَبُولُهَا عِنْدَ وُجُودِهَا.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَيَثْبُتُ المِلْكُ فِيهَا مِنْ حِينِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَالوَصِيَّةُ بِخِلَافِ ذَلِكَ كُلِّهِ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>